// T1295: mutating through a `place!` unwrap on a `none` Optional[Vector[T]]
// emits the presence-check panic (the panic branch is a fresh emission inside
// optionalPayloadReceiverSlot, not a reuse of genOptionalForceUnwrap).
main() `test(expected: """panic: unwrap failed: optional is none""") {
  int[]? a = none;
  a!.push(1);
}
